{"tid":1933234,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"2017遊記-西班牙+南法之旅","createTime":"2020-03-19T07:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T12:44:32.000Z","uid":244641,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dd4b99ddb81837b8c34cb3e5fcd876d62f1c4f60","tid":1933234,"uid":244641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:29:04.000Z","msg":"Hi又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />眼見連登好似冇乜南法/西班牙既遊記<br />\n決定share 少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由於當初冇諗住寫遊記 未必有我上一篇摩洛哥咁詳盡<br />\n加上我地hea遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盡量會放多d圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次唔係自己去 同行朋友（陳仔）1位<br />\n<br />\n精選出黎主要行程有<br />\n西班牙（馬德里-Sevilla鬥牛之旅-ibiza-巴塞）<br />\n南法薰衣草遊 同 尼斯<br />\n加多少少瑞士少女峰<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n飛機選擇阿提哈德航空（Etihad Airways）埋單$ 6K幾左右<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n落機第一餐<br />\n煙肉tapas 陳仔食三文魚<br />\n西班牙人好中意小食多餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k5tVo70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk5tVo70.jpg&h=d43b5257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行食完放抵行李就去附近既馬德里主廣場Plaza Mayor<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0QMcrnV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0QMcrnV.jpg&h=b8daad6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WRzmjHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWRzmjHY.jpg&h=c275385e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廣場附近既<br />\n<br />\n聖米蓋爾市場San Miguel Market <br />\n D人好chill 咁係入面嘆紅酒 食下野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5XdyaQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5XdyaQQ.jpg&h=45f9883f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZKE9tCL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZKE9tCL.jpg&h=67aef32d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地就冇幫襯 打個白鴿轉就走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VhGDmYM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVhGDmYM.jpg&h=b49da603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n差唔多到王宮既時候有賊仔想偷我銀包比我發現咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我同fd就停低扮影相 佢地都知道失敗咗就急急腳走 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HUL1jMa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHUL1jMa.jpg&h=1a2f671c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3yXSrre.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yXSrre.jpg&h=d0a12425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬德里王宮Palacio Real de Madrid<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZ4QXyr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZ4QXyr.jpg&h=bb8ea913&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bBhGjMP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbBhGjMP.jpg&h=88cf4e09&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C8nnOFd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC8nnOFd.jpg&h=6045d279&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PDzp10g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPDzp10g.jpg&h=4cf03f68&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bc0410k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbc0410k.jpg&h=232fd26f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去歐洲都不外乎教堂皇宮等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />參觀完就返酒店訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一日就普通市區觀光 同買火車飛<br />\n就係因為火車站條友對我地態度好西 令我好憎馬德里d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係主廣場食咗個Paella ⋯⋯好難食 呃旅客<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kBp5Mu9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkBp5Mu9.jpg&h=7d0f008a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n40度都幾係野<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R2Zxrvo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR2Zxrvo.jpg&h=1e9dbfba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n Temple of Debod<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n4aQdaD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn4aQdaD.jpg&h=e13c36b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上成日都係公園/商場逗留<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dCGDm4n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdCGDm4n.jpg&h=7047d10a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s7V8KhO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs7V8KhO.jpg&h=8909932e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mHv8KhY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmHv8KhY.jpg&h=1b41b027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係馬德里留咗2晚 對呢個城市冇咩好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完！"},{"pid":"fb0d2e07946448c3f1a03ca796dd268f0f909d64","tid":1933234,"uid":145361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:19:34.000Z","msg":"啲相好似執多得滯 純粹個人意見 anyway support <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743313f2b56fa337da1f64645730335fe3adf39d","tid":1933234,"uid":244641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb0d2e07946448c3f1a03ca796dd268f0f909d64","tid":1933234,"uid":145361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:19:34.000Z","msg":"啲相好似執多得滯 純粹個人意見 anyway support <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T15:47:49.000Z","msg":"呢批